## Getting Started

1.  **Install dependencies:**

    ```bash
    pip install -r requirements.txt
    ```

2.  **Run the application:**

    ```bash
    uvicorn src.main:app --reload
    ```

3.  **Run with Docker:**

    ```bash
    docker build -t {{ .Project.Name }} .
    docker run -p 8000:8000 {{ .Project.Name }}
    ```

